item.description:
Romance : Untold (stylized in all-caps) is the second full-length album by ENHYPEN. It was released on July 12, 2024 with "XO (Only If You Say Yes)" serving as the album's title track.
The physical album comes in 12 versions: Inceptio, Arcanum, Concessio, seven individual Engene versions, Weverse and vinyl.

  2. "XO (Only If You Say Yes)" - 3:08

  4. "Hundred Broken Hearts" - 3:21
  5. "Brought The Heat Back" - 2:56
  6. "Paranormal" - 2:35
